			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As a Scout, I know it is my main objective in a group to co-ordinate HO's (sorta like a pimp in RL). Most people in the game have never seen a group HO completed so have no idea that it is not better than the solo HO's that they are trying to get off before someone else hits a button and breaks their solo started chain.
<br />

<br />
How do you go about preping a group for using group HO's?
<br />
It seems like it would be easy in a guild group, but anyone who has not seen them thinks I am crazy.<br />_________________<br />Asher
<br />
Scout Member of Elysium
<br />
Server Crushbone</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
